												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/sarahadler/">Sarah Adler</a></h6>
													Sarah Adler is a writer & arts organizer living in Philadelphia. She received her MFA in creative nonfiction from the University of Iowa Nonfiction Writing. Her essay, “Emmy’s Chorus” was recently published in <em>The Iowa Review</em>.																									</div>
